				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\mathrm{CRF}=\frac{i\times (1+i{)}^{n}}{(1+i{)}^{n}-1}$$\end{document}where n represents the plant lifetime (i.e., 25 years) and i the rate of interest rate (Bejan et al. 1996; Dinçer et al. 2017). In Eq. (12), PECk\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
