				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${f}_{b,k}=\frac{{\dot{Y}}_{k}}{{\dot{Y}}_{k}+{b}_{f,k}\cdot \dot{E}{x}_{D,k}}$$\end{document}

The relative difference in environmental impact is given by Eq. (25) (Cavalcanti 2017).25rbk=bP,k-bF,kbF,k=1-εkεk+Y˙kbf,k·E˙xP,k\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$r{b}_{k}=\frac{{b}_{P,k}-{b}_{F,k}}{{b}_{F,k}}=\frac{1-{\varepsilon }_{k}}{{\varepsilon }_{k}}+\frac{{\dot{Y}}_{k}}{{b}_{f,k}\cdot \dot{E}{x}_{P,k}}$$\end{document}

